{"id": "1288521315325837312", "channel_id": "1288480962656731158", "type": 19, "author_id": "773037463626317887", "author_name": "fengtengjayden9754", "author_bot": false, "content": "了解，谢谢您的建议！\n从2024年8月31日入坑至今，我已经攒了198个无垢之芯。\n以30抽必定获得指定命轮的机制，我足够抽取到三叠位巨人之刃了。\n我稍后会去狂躁蜡馆刷“扭曲双子•白“。\n估计反击型凯刻斯应该很快就会成型。", "timestamp": "2024-09-25T15:23:41.142000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["771169877121564703"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1288521314792902746", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-25-23-02-01-52_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 113792, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288480962656731158/1288521314792902746/Screenshot_2024-09-25-23-02-01-52_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbe6fd&is=69ca957d&hm=f4fd7e1d24a9659cb429491bef806835f5bd0c5680e8d7816e95fead01c3c44d&"}, {"id": "1288521315099218012", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-25-23-12-22-81_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 98375, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288480962656731158/1288521315099218012/Screenshot_2024-09-25-23-12-22-81_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbe6fd&is=69ca957d&hm=b7a7c40e68d066ad3b1e48ee9c7778bb38b6feb9e4e2ab642acd5462cbe6c1de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1288488549397823488", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288480962656731158", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "请问凯刻斯适合装备什么密契和命轮？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1288521469474902077", "channel_id": "1288480962656731158", "type": 19, "author_id": "773037463626317887", "author_name": "fengtengjayden9754", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢您的指导！\n\n目前我在调查行动（主线剧情关卡）使用的队伍是哈姆林，凯刻斯，戈利亚和拉蒙娜。\n而在幕间演习，我通常会使用其他巨佬提供的莱克和图鲁助阵。\n\n以调查行动的配队，或许我暂时将凯刻斯培养成辅助生存角色，而不是反击角色会较好。\n请问我应该给定位是辅助生存的凯刻斯装备什么命轮呢？\n不知“资讯就是生命”和“不存在之地”是否合适？", "timestamp": "2024-09-25T15:24:17.894000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["699270788578148442"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1288521468631846952", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-29-52-37_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 116081, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288480962656731158/1288521468631846952/Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-29-52-37_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbe721&is=69ca95a1&hm=5d73d8f41488d4a208eb83aa1e126eba0da2ea6f789b0b7f8275734bfcdf496f&"}, {"id": "1288521468929380362", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-41-17-38_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 144821, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288480962656731158/1288521468929380362/Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-41-17-38_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbe721&is=69ca95a1&hm=a41da6bb2cd148a3db7f4ef2484d2a68f6882020e56878cdf87775332a15ef08&"}, {"id": "1288521469240017048", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-41-27-80_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142529, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1288480962656731158/1288521469240017048/Screenshot_2024-09-25-22-41-27-80_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbe721&is=69ca95a1&hm=32be6761d5c96d5071d1c9b465be25798b2a384194da7a8ec982fbeef1d61037&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1288487640475242537", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288480962656731158", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "请问凯刻斯适合装备什么密契和命轮？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["11811681586782